  "attachmentHtml": "\n<p><strong>PC Number: </strong>2008-1919<br></p><p><strong>Date: </strong>2008-12-12</p><hr><p>\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.33in;text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nWhereas the Honourable Louise Lamarre Proulx,\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.33in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\na Judge of the Tax Court of Canada, who has continued in judicial\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.33in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\noffice for at least fifteen years, has tendered her resignation effective\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.33in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nNovember 15, 2008 and, as of this date, her combined age and number\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.33in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nof years in judicial office is not less than eighty; \n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.33in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.33in;text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nTherefore, Her Excellency the Governor General\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.33in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nin Council, on the recommendation of the Minister of Justice, hereby:\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.33in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.83in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n(<em>a</em>) accepts the resignation of the Honourable Louise Lamarre Proulx; and \n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.83in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.83in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n(<em>b</em>) pursuant to paragraph 42(1)(<em>a</em>)<em>&nbsp;</em>of the <em>Judges Act</em>, grants her\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.83in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nan annuity of $173,333.33 commencing on November 15, 2008\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.83in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nand continuing during her life.\n</p>\n<br style=\"page-break-before:always\">\n<p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nAttendu que l'honorable Louise Lamarre Proulx,\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\njuge de la Cour canadienne de l’impôt, après avoir exercé des fonctions judiciaires pendant au moins quinze ans, a donné sa démission, laquelle\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nprend effet le 15 novembre 2008, et que, à cette date, le chiffre obtenu\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\npar l’addition de son âge et du nombre d’années d’exercice est d’au moins\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nquatre-vingt,\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nÀ ces causes, sur recommandation du ministre de la Justice,\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nSon Excellence la Gouverneure générale en conseil :\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n<em>a</em>) accepte la démission de l'honorable Louise Lamarre Proulx;\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n<em>b</em>) en vertu de l'alinéa 42(1)<em>a</em>) de la <em>Loi sur les juges</em>, lui accorde,\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nà titre viager, une pension annuelle de 173 333,33 $, payable à\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\ncompter du 15 novembre 2008.\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p>\n\n<p></p><form method=\"post\" action=\"index.php\"><input type=\"submit\" value=\"Back to Form\" class=\"btn btn-primary\" name=\"return\"></form>\t\t\n        <!-- end main content -->\n        <div id=\"def-preFooter\">\n       \t\t<!-- Write closure fall-back static file -->\n             <!--Response.Write readFile(\"StaticFallbackFiles/gcweb/preFooter-\" & $lang & \".html\") -->\n        </div>\n\t\t<!-- Write closure template -->\n        <script type=\"text/javascript\">\n            var defPreFooter = document.getElementById(\"def-preFooter\");\n            defPreFooter.outerHTML = wet.builder.preFooter({\n                cdnEnv: \"prod\",\n                dateModified: \"2022-07-11\",\n                showPostContent: true\n            });\n        </script>\n    "
